===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''draughts''' ''singular''

#(''UK'') {{uncountable}} A [[game]] for two [[player]]s played on a [[chessboard]] in which the players each have 12 pieces, known as ''[[man|men]]'', and the [[object]] is to [[capture]] each of the [[opponent]]'s pieces by jumping one's own pieces over the opponent's pieces. (See [[w:draughts|the Wikipedia page]] for the full rules of the game. There are various variants of the game.)

